description: Horse Mask,Designed with comfort and convenience in mind. This generously measured horse mask slips easily on and off the horses head for a secure and comfortable fit; The horse mask can even be worn over a halter. The soft mesh protects the eyes and ears while providing full visibility. This horse mask won't be too tight ,horse can open their eyes. This horse mask uses nylon fabric that covers the face from the horse's ear to the forehead. The one-piece mask without any hook and loop fasteners. Easy to wear during the process will not stimulate the horse. The secure fit of this mask makes it a great option for the horse that tends to remove traditional, strap-on masks. , which makes the product have better tensile properties and better handle.
